
|YKOCurrently, Darkwind does not support spells for players without guilds.
The exception is the introductory Dark Wind powers. Unguilded newbies through
level 5 may use |YKBncot, ndomain, nkick, npunch|YKO and |YKBnheal|YKO.
Players from levels 6 through 49 may use their adventurer forms:
|YKBacot, adomain, akick, apunch|YKO and |YKBaheal|YKO.

While fighting, characters through level 20 may occasionally feel the Dark
Wind refresh a small amount of SP. Both its chance and strength taper with
level.

